data.description: BEST LOCATION with a New Roof!!!!, in a highly desired area in a well-situated family neighborhood. Centrally located, 7,500 sqft, with an open floor plan: 4 BED, 2 BATH. The patio area, is perfect for entertaining family and friends. A Great Home To Raise Your Family. The exterior includes a screened patio and couple of fruit trees and a fenced yard This amazing opportunity has also a Fully Independent Efficiency (1 BED/1 BATH). The property is within minutes from schools, parks, shops, and the turnpike Way, which makes it very easy to commute!!!
